    "description": "<strong>我们希望有更多热爱这类型游戏的朋友们可以参与到试玩并给出任何游戏反馈，大家的支持是团队的最大动力！感谢！<br>《冬日生存工程》交流QQ群：908471161</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174500/extras/c7c5e558d128aa5298d1604e908149c5.webp?t=1772122244\" width=615 height=59 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174500/extras/7e1357076ec3508af7fb705c53ced1c3.poster.avif?t=1772122244\" width=614 height=298 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174500/extras/7e1357076ec3508af7fb705c53ced1c3.webm?t=1772122244\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174500/extras/7e1357076ec3508af7fb705c53ced1c3.mp4?t=1772122244\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>在末日的废墟中，生存不仅仅是一种选择，而是一场无尽的考验。这是一款多人联机丧尸生存游戏，带你进入一个被丧尸和严酷环境支配的末世世界。你将扮演一名末日之中的幸存者，在这个人间炼狱中奋力求生，探索城市废墟，面对极端的温度变化和各种未知的威胁。</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174500/extras/85ceeeb75ea5e6f59ed3fea99eee5700.webp?t=1772122244\" width=615 height=59 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174500/extras/f761662e3ed91a97e440715e239e7ee0.poster.avif?t=1772122244\" width=614 height=296 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174500/extras/f761662e3ed91a97e440715e239e7ee0.webm?t=1772122244\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174500/extras/f761662e3ed91a97e440715e239e7ee0.mp4?t=1772122244\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>一夜之间你所在的城市爆发了丧尸危机，整座城市成为一片人间炼狱，同时气温也在一步步的降低，在躲过了最初的混乱之后你决心逃离城市返回家人身边从而踏上了归家之旅，旅途中你能依靠的就是临时安身之所的载具与手中的武器去解开这一切的谜题从而找到逃离这处绝境的关键。</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174500/extras/51d44842050ac2fdacd23f0ea2ada304.webp?t=1772122244\" width=615 height=59 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174500/extras/43e45e0835dfa4c9146705bc1e3afb2c.poster.avif?t=1772122244\" width=614 height=296 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174500/extras/43e45e0835dfa4c9146705bc1e3afb2c.webm?t=1772122244\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174500/extras/43e45e0835dfa4c9146705bc1e3afb2c.mp4?t=1772122244\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>你将一个人或带领你的伙伴自由探索这片沦为末日的世界，建造安全的营地，种植作物维持生存，同时维修载具、制作武器，去探索一个个危险的据点与废墟，获取更多的物资，提升自己的装备，在这片充满丧尸与未知怪物的末日环境下尽可能地生存下去。</strong>",
